fields.description:
Right from the beginning of Patta, graphic t-shirts have always been as important to us, as our sneaker drops and collaborative releases. They serve as a street canvas for us to get our message across to people. Giving you and us a voice out there on the corners. Speaking up for what we believe in. Together as a family. For our Spring Summer 2023 season this has not changed, with a wide assortment of high quality graphic tees included. The Patta Pattassium T-Shirt is produced in 180gsm cotton. It features a screen printed Patta script logo at the left hand side of the chest. The back is adorned with a screen printed Pattassium artwork.
